{
  "stem": "11552.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before we left Buczacz, my mother, my little brother, and I, my mother told us, if we are ever separated, that we should not go back to the place where we came from, but return to Buczacz.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We will meet in Buczacz because we know the area, we know the villages, we know the forest, that somehow along the line, we should go back there and not back to Kopyczynce, or not back to wherever we will be.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was going to Buczacz, and I was, on the way, as I was going, I was working in the fields, I went out and begged for work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is how I got a little bit of bread, and some potatoes, and some of the sour milk, what they call, it's like buttermilk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I came back to Buczacz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I didn't know what happened to Milek.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was sure that Milek died there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and fields.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fields.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like weeding the weeds out of potatoes and all the other things that were growing in the ground, and other weeding.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, one, there was a girl who thought-- she was quite nasty to me in one of the fields.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I pretended to be a refugee going into the other direction, not going to Buczacz, going from Buczacz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if I was going from Kopyczynce, they could suspect because they knew what was happening, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They probably heard the shooting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I pretended that I was going to join my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes they believed me, sometimes they didn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But one of the girls didn't believe me, but she gave me some potatoes, anyway.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I pretend-- I spoke the Ukrainian language perfectly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I spoke Polish perfectly.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
